        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[澳大利亚就中国招募澳前飞行员报道展开调查]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>澳大利亚正在调查有关中国军方试图招募前澳洲防军飞行员提供训练服务的报道，并且发现“足够的证据”，认为此问题值得深入调查。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>据彭博社报道，澳洲</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>国防部长</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>马勒斯</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>星期三（11月9日）在堪培拉告诉记者，国防部初步调查发现了“足够的证据”，值得对这个问题进行深入调查。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>马勒斯指出，</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>任何前军人透露政府的秘密信息，都是显而易见、明白无误的犯罪。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<section id="imu"><div id="dfp-ad-imu1">
        
</div>


</section>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>他说：“国防活动、人员和资产，成为外国情报部门的目标，这已经不是秘密。”</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>英国国防部几周之前也表示，正立即采取措施来遏制和惩罚这种行为。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>BBC在10月中旬报道称，多达30名曾在英国军队服役的人员，正在向中国军人传授他们的专业技能。报道援引一位不具名西方官员的说法，称一些教练员的酬劳约27万美元（约37.78万新元）。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

<div id="innity-in-post"></div>
<div id="dfp-ad-midarticlespecial">
        
</div>



<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>马勒斯在</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>10月份也</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>要求澳洲国防部调查澳洲飞行员被中国境内运营的一家南非飞行学校聘用一事。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>马勒斯</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>表示，澳洲将检视当前的国防政策和程序，但没有具体说明需要多长时间或正在审查多少案件。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
      


